Hmmm... Here we're removing the root process time from the map, only to add its value later in:
return ImmutableProcessTime.copyOf(rootProcessTime)
                           .withDelayBetweenSteps(rootProcessTime.getDelayBetweenSteps() + overallDelayBetweenSteps);

We can do just processTimesWithoutRootProcess.get(correlationId); and then construct the result as:
return ImmutableProcessTime.copyOf(rootProcessTime)
                           .withDelayBetweenSteps(overallDelayBetweenSteps);

